Package: wendy
Type: Package
Title: Weak Form Estimation of Nonlinear Dynamics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jack", "Krebsbach",
      email = "jack.krebsbach@colorado.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Parameter estimation for ordinary differential equations (ODEs)
    using weak form estimation. WENDy avoids numerical differentiation of noisy
    data by leveraging integration by parts with compactly supported test
    functions.
